  "title": "TheBrewingProject",
  "description": "Custom beverage crafting, with large customizability on the drinking effects.",
  "body": "# <div align=\"center\">TheBrewingProject</div>\n#### <div align=\"center\">A complete rewrite of [BreweryX](https://modrinth.com/plugin/breweryx)</div>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bde1694f3a8d7edbfc193768db4d85dc9f351ebd.png\" />\n\n### <div align=\"center\">A lenient alternate crafting process for alcoholic and nonalcoholic drinks</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  \n| [Documentation](https://tbp.breweryteam.dev/docs/welcome/) | [Source Code](https://github.com/BreweryTeam/TheBrewingProject) | [Development Builds](https://ci.breweryteam.dev/job/BreweryTeam/job/TheBrewingProject/job/master/) | [Discord Server](https://discord.gg/3FkNaNDnta) |\n|---|---|---|---|\n\n</div><br><br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n<h3>Mix / Cook</h3>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://tbp.breweryteam.dev/docs/for-players/brewing/mixing-and-cooking/\">\n    Learn more →\n  </a>\n</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0333b14e4b5d1519f9cf574afdfe45890687ae35_0.webp\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<br><br>\n\n<h3>Distill</h3>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://tbp.breweryteam.dev/docs/for-players/brewing/distilling/\">\n    Learn more →\n  </a>\n</p>\n<img src=\"https://tbp.breweryteam.dev/_astro/distillery-inputs-and-outputs.Ci7O6Qkf_ZMMGDy.webp\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<br><br>\n\n<h3>Age</h3>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://tbp.breweryteam.dev/docs/for-players/brewing/aging/\">\n    Learn more →\n  </a>\n</p>\n<img src=\"https://tbp.breweryteam.dev/_astro/small-barrel.DYQgmmj1_17WiMd.webp\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<img src=\"https://tbp.breweryteam.dev/_astro/large-barrel.Dg2_SDU-_1AIEKR.webp\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<br><br>\n\n<h3>Babble</h3>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c469f18f75133d7e0d33e825c94b2b77c979bb01_0.webp\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<br>\n\n<h3>Hallucinate</h3>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b40c6be790f3fa35d11c6aa6272e3db4a2b0dd8e_0.webp\" width=\"70%\">\n\n<br>\n\n<h3>Puke</h3>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d3cf0f3728ee35d63c633a81782cb31d13794819.png\" width=\"70%\">\n<h4>..and so much more :o</h4>\n\n<br><br>\n\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n\n### See for yourself!\n\nWe have a demo server where you can easily brew and drink, with no setup required whatsoever.\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/03bb3cda4d64c5ab609d5651a299b8616d108270.png\" width=\"85%\">\n\n#### [showcase.breweryteam.dev](https://mcsrvstat.us/server/showcase.breweryteam.dev)\n\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n</div>",
